%N A393411 Expansion of e.g.f. (1/x) * Series_Reversion( x/(1 + 3*x)^(2/3) ).
%F A393411 E.g.f. A(x) satisfies A(x) = (1 + 3*x*A(x))^(2/3).
%F A393411 a(n) = 3^n * n! * binomial(2*(n+1)/3,n)/(n+1).
%F A393411 a(3*n+2) = 0 for n > 0.
%o A393411 (PARI) a(n) = 3^n*n!*binomial(2*(n+1)/3, n)/(n+1);
